        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0126-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T21:04:06.671+09:00">Chang Tsung-t'ung p. 15: 3334 </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T19:07:36.79+09:00">4444</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T19:12:27.61+09:00">4444　地　－ia</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T21:04:42.547+09:00">義　－ia</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T21:57:13.62+09:00">老　－og</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-17a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T19:12:50.364+09:00">巧　－og</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_006-18a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2021-03-13T19:15:05.689+09:00">遊　－og</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:37:17.018+09:00">Lao Dan said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-9a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:37:54.925+09:00">At that point Confucius unwrapped his twelve classics and set about explaining them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-9a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:38:06.955+09:00">Lao Dan interrupted his explanation:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-9a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:38:20.055+09:00">and he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-9a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:38:41.55+09:00">"You are being too long-winded:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_013-9a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-03-24T00:39:07.086+09:00">I wish I could hear from you the main point."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:31:16.572+09:00">"To make me the Son of Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:32:17.143+09:00">would be fine by me.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:33:15.378+09:00">However, I'm suffering from a terrible illness</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:33:30.918+09:00">and for the moment I have to look after that:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:40:14.435+09:00">I have no time for this world of yours.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:35:33.364+09:00">Now the world is of of ultimate importance</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:36:48.652+09:00">but for its sake one will not harm one's life,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:37:10.116+09:00">and how much less for other things.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:37:43.809+09:00">Only to those who don't give a damn about the world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:38:04.188+09:00">can one entrust the care of the world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:42:57.879+09:00">When Shun was ceding the world to Zizhou Zhibo</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:38:48.423+09:00">Zizhou Zhibo said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:39:13.938+09:00">"It just so happens that  I have a truly terrific illness</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:39:27.835+09:00">and for the time being I have to look after that,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:40:08.16+09:00">I have no time for this world of yours."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:41:14.557+09:00">So one can see that the world may be a large object</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:41:44.315+09:00">but that for the sake of it one will not make light of one's life.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:42:32.945+09:00">This s where those who have achieved the Way differ from ordinary people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:43:09.837+09:00">When Shun was ceding the world to Shan Juan</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:43:16.85+09:00">Shan Juan said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:43:37.461+09:00">"I find myself at the centre of the universe</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:44:53.568+09:00">for the winter days I dress in skin and wool,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:45:23.182+09:00">for the summer I dress in plain vine ad hemp;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:45:43.007+09:00">in spring I do my planting,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_028-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#guest" modified="2021-06-25T16:45:57.363+09:00">and my physical frame is strong enough for the work.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_033-3a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-03-24T17:51:53.019+09:00">so that the overarching system of the ancients,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_033-3a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-03-24T17:59:37.08+09:00">and the Art of the Way was increasingly torn apart by everyone.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_033-3a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-03-24T17:49:57.933+09:00">The scholars of later generations</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0126_tls_033-3a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-03-24T17:51:11.038+09:00">unfortunately had no eyes for the purity of (the universe of) Heaven and Earth</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
